{"id": "figure_016", "modality": "figures", "name": "Vision Transformer (ViT)", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces the Vision Transformer (ViT) figure. Title 'Vision Transformer (Dosovitskiy et al., 2021)'. Show: an input image split into a 3x3 grid of 9 equal patches; each patch -> linear projection into a row of 9 equal-width patch-embedding tokens; a prepended [CLS] token (10 tokens total) each summed with a position embedding (0..9) drawn as small stacked chips; the token row feeding a Transformer Encoder block (Multi-Head Attention -> Add&Norm -> MLP -> Add&Norm, labeled 'L x') ; the [CLS] output -> an MLP head -> 'class'. Include the equation z_0 = [x_class; x_p^1 E; ...; x_p^N E] + E_pos.", "requirements": ["An input image is split into a 3x3 grid of 9 equal-size patches, aligned", "Exactly 9 patch-embedding tokens plus one [CLS] token (10) appear in one aligned row of equal-width tokens", "Each token is summed with a position-embedding chip numbered consistently (0..9)", "The Transformer encoder block shows MHA -> Add&Norm -> MLP -> Add&Norm in order, labeled with a repeat 'L x'", "The [CLS] output connects to an MLP head producing a 'class' output", "The embedding equation renders its subscripts/superscripts (x_p^1, E_pos) correctly", "No element overlaps any other; arrows do not pass through unrelated block labels", "All sibling tokens/patches are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters", "The whole figure fits in 1920x1080 with no scrollbar", "A legend maps every block color and arrow style; each major block has a tensor-shape annotation; nothing clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 3, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 2, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5967, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 15901}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4881, "rv_n_defects": 2, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 1, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 24030}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4968, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 34135}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_016_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_016_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vision Transformer (ViT)</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 30px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .equation {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;\n            color: #34495e;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Vision Transformer (Dosovitskiy et al., 2021)</div>\n        \n        <svg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1080\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" fill=\"url(#bgGradient)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Gradients and Patterns -->\n            <defs>\n                <linearGradient id=\"bgGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f8f9fa\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e9ecef\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"patchGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#3498db\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#2980b9\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"tokenGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#e74c3c\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#c0392b\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"clsGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f39c12\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e67e22\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"transformerGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#9b59b6\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#8e44ad\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"mlpGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#27ae60\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#229954\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Input Image -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"150\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 Grid on Image -->\n            <g stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\">\n                <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"390\"/>\n                <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"390\"/>\n                <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"230\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"230\"/>\n                <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"310\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"310\"/>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Patch Numbers -->\n            <g font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"195\">1</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"195\">2</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"195\">3</text>\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"275\">4</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"275\">5</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"275\">6</text>\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"355\">7</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"355\">8</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"355\">9</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow from Image to Linear Projection -->\n            <path d=\"M 350 270 Q 400 270 450 270\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Linear Projection</text>\n            \n            <!-- Patch Embeddings (9 tokens) -->\n            <g>\n                <text x=\"600\" y=\"140\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Patch Embeddings</text>\n                \n                <!-- 9 patch embedding tokens -->\n                <g>\n                    <rect x=\"480\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2081\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"530\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"550\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2082\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"580\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"600\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2083\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"630\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"650\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2084\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"680\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"700\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2085\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"730\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"750\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2086\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"780\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2087\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"830\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"850\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2088\u1d56E</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"880\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"900\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2089\u1d56E</text>\n                </g>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- CLS Token (prepended) -->\n            <rect x=\"420\" y=\"200\" width=\"40\" height=\"120\" fill=\"url(#clsGradient)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"440\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">[CLS]</text>\n            <text x=\"440\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e67e22\">CLS Token</text>\n            \n            <!-- Position Embeddings (small chips) -->\n            <g>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Position Embeddings</text>\n                \n                <!-- Position embedding chips -->\n                <g fill=\"#95a5a6\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"1\">\n                    <rect x=\"430\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"440\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">0</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"490\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">1</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"540\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"550\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">2</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"590\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"600\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">3</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"640\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"650\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">4</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"690\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"700\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">5</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"740\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"750\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">6</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"790\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">7</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"840\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"850\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">8</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"890\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"900\" y=\"352\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">9</text>\n                </g>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Plus signs for addition -->\n            <g font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n                <text x=\"440\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"500\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"550\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"600\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"650\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"700\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"750\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"800\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"850\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n                <text x=\"900\" y=\"335\">+</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow to Transformer -->\n            <path d=\"M 680 400 Q 680 450 680 500\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Transformer Encoder Block -->\n            <g>\n                <rect x=\"580\" y=\"520\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" fill=\"url(#transformerGradient)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"510\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#8e44ad\">Transformer Encoder</text>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#8e44ad\">L \u00d7</text>\n                \n                <!-- Multi-Head Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"540\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Multi-Head Attention</text>\n                \n                <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"610\" width=\"160\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"630\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Add & Norm</text>\n                \n                <!-- MLP -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"660\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"690\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MLP</text>\n                \n                <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"730\" width=\"160\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"680\" y=\"750\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Add & Norm</text>\n                \n                <!-- Residual connections -->\n                <g stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\">\n                    <path d=\"M 590 565 Q 570 565 570 625 Q 570 625 590 625\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 590 685 Q 570 685 570 745 Q 570 745 590 745\"/>\n                </g>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow from Transformer to MLP Head -->\n            <path d=\"M 680 840 Q 680 890 680 940\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"720\" y=\"890\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">CLS output only</text>\n            \n            <!-- MLP Head -->\n            <rect x=\"600\" y=\"960\" width=\"160\" height=\"60\" fill=\"url(#mlpGradient)\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"985\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">MLP Head</text>\n            <text x=\"680\" y=\"1005\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">(Classification)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow to Class -->\n            <path d=\"M 780 990 Q 830 990 880 990\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Class Output -->\n            <rect x=\"920\" y=\"970\" width=\"80\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"995\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">class</text>\n            \n            <!-- Equation -->\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-family=\"Times New Roman, serif\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-style=\"italic\">\n                z\u2080 = [x_class; x\u2081\u1d56E; x\u2082\u1d56E; ...; x\u2089\u1d56E] + E_pos\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Legend -->\n            <g transform=\"translate(1200, 200)\">\n                <text x=\"0\" y=\"0\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Legend:</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"20\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#clsGradient)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"30\" y=\"35\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">CLS Token</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"50\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"30\" y=\"65\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Patch Embeddings</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"80\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" stroke=\"#7f8c8d\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"30\" y=\"95\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Position Embeddings</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"110\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#transformerGradient)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"30\" y=\"125\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Transformer Encoder</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"0\" y=\"140\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"url(#mlpGradient)\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"30\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">MLP Head</text>\n            </g>\n            \n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vision Transformer (ViT)</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 30px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .equation {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;\n            color: #34495e;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <svg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1080\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" fill=\"url(#bgGradient)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Gradients and Patterns -->\n            <defs>\n                <linearGradient id=\"bgGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f8f9fa\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e9ecef\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"patchGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#3498db\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#2980b9\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"tokenGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#e74c3c\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#c0392b\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"clsGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#f39c12\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#e67e22\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"transformerGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#9b59b6\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#8e44ad\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <linearGradient id=\"mlpGradient\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n                    <stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#27ae60\"/>\n                    <stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#229954\"/>\n                </linearGradient>\n                \n                <!-- Arrow markers -->\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Title -->\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"60\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"48\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Vision Transformer (Dosovitskiy et al., 2021)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Input Image -->\n            <rect x=\"80\" y=\"120\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"200\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input Image</text>\n            \n            <!-- 3x3 Grid on Image -->\n            <g stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\">\n                <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"360\"/>\n                <line x1=\"240\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"360\"/>\n                <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"200\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"200\"/>\n                <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"280\"/>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Patch Numbers -->\n            <g font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"165\">1</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"165\">2</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"165\">3</text>\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"245\">4</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"245\">5</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"245\">6</text>\n                <text x=\"120\" y=\"325\">7</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"325\">8</text>\n                <text x=\"280\" y=\"325\">9</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow from Image to Linear Projection -->\n            <path d=\"M 350 240 Q 400 240 450 240\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"400\" y=\"225\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Linear Projection</text>\n            \n            <!-- Patch Embeddings -->\n            <g>\n                <!-- CLS Token -->\n                <rect x=\"410\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#clsGradient)\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"440\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">[CLS]</text>\n                \n                <!-- 9 Patch Tokens -->\n                <rect x=\"480\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"550\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"620\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"690\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"760\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"830\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"900\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"970\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <rect x=\"1040\" y=\"170\" width=\"60\" height=\"140\" fill=\"url(#patchGradient)\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Token Labels -->\n                <text x=\"510\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2081\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"580\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2082\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"650\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2083\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"720\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2084\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"790\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2085\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"860\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2086\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"930\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2087\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"1000\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2088\u1d56E</text>\n                <text x=\"1070\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">x\u2089\u1d56E</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Position Embeddings -->\n            <g>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">+ Position Embeddings</text>\n                \n                <!-- Position embedding chips -->\n                <rect x=\"430\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"430\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"440\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2080</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"500\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"500\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"510\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2081</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"570\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"570\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"580\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2082</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"640\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"640\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"650\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2083</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"710\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"710\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"720\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2084</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"780\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"780\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"790\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2085</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"850\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"850\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"860\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2086</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"920\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"920\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"930\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2087</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"990\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"990\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"1000\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2088</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"330\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#95a5a6\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <rect x=\"1060\" y=\"340\" width=\"20\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" rx=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"1070\" y=\"360\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">E\u2089</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow to Transformer -->\n            <path d=\"M 725 380 Q 725 420 725 460\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Transformer Encoder Block -->\n            <g>\n                <rect x=\"580\" y=\"480\" width=\"290\" height=\"240\" fill=\"url(#transformerGradient)\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"12\"/>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Transformer Encoder</text>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"white\">L \u00d7</text>\n                \n                <!-- Multi-Head Attention -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"540\" width=\"250\" height=\"35\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"562\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Multi-Head Attention</text>\n                \n                <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"585\" width=\"250\" height=\"25\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"602\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n                \n                <!-- MLP -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"620\" width=\"250\" height=\"35\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"642\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">MLP</text>\n                \n                <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n                <rect x=\"600\" y=\"665\" width=\"250\" height=\"25\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"725\" y=\"682\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n            </g>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow from Transformer to MLP Head -->\n            <path d=\"M 580 600 Q 520 600 460 600\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"520\" y=\"585\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">[CLS] output</text>\n            \n            <!-- MLP Head -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"560\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"url(#mlpGradient)\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"590\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">MLP</text>\n            <text x=\"380\" y=\"610\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Head</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow to Class -->\n            <path d=\"M 320 600 Q 270 600 220 600\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Class Output -->\n            <rect x=\"120\" y=\"570\" width=\"80\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"160\" y=\"605\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">class</text>\n            \n            <!-- Equation -->\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"800\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"24\" font-family=\"Times New Roman, serif\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-style=\"italic\">\n                z\u2080 = [x_class; x\u2081\u1d56E; x\u2082\u1d56E; ...; x\u2089\u1d56E] + E_pos\n            </text>\n            \n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}